01:19:58,208 --> 01:19:59,208
Kecuali kau.

1332
01:19:59,916 --> 01:20:02,125
Kau akan diingat selamanya.

1333
01:20:02,208 --> 01:20:04,208
Karena beberapa hal abadi.

